<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shrink-v">shrink <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ʃrɪŋk/    美 /ʃrɪŋk/  </p>
<p>(shrank / shrunk, shrunk)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1vi-vt">1.<strong>vi &amp; vt (使) 缩水；(使) 收缩：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Will this shirt shrink in the wash?
这件衬衫洗后会缩水吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The hot water shrank my sweater.
我的毛衣遇热水后收缩了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-vi-vt">2.★ <strong>vi &amp; vt (使) 缩小；减少；贬值：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The crowd shrinks as some people slide away.
随着一些人悄悄离开，人群缩小了。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Internet in a sense has shrunk the world.
从某种意义上来说，互联网把世界缩小了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3vi">3.<strong>vi 退缩；畏缩</strong></h4></div>